nodes.text: Miiliki-spoorr Lingsnot was an Adnerem female and member of the Lingsnot family. She once underwent a Spleen Corrosion surgery and spent many hours recovering on her home Gravity Resuscitation Track. After this incident, she managed to attend many charities, including Offspring of Parents Who Haven't Been Born Yet, her personal favorite.

Miiliki-spoorr Lingsnot was featured in Monsters and Aliens from George Lucas, a book published in 1993. Lucasfilm employee Leland Chee, who maintains the Holocron continuity database, has indicated that information contained in the book is non-canonical.
